Package tracker.GuiComponents.Containers

Class SinglePromptDisplay

  • java.lang.Object
    • tracker.GuiComponents.Containers.SinglePromptDisplay
  • public class SinglePromptDisplay
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Nolan Rochon This creates all components needed for asking a single prompt. Spacing is done to allow up to 4 on each page.
